== XC Ski Trail Report App ==

An android application for downloading and displaying xc ski trail reports.

This project is not affiliated with skinnyski.com, or any website or trail manager.  Do not contact any website provider with questions or issues with this application.  All included reports are Copyright their respective site owners and subject to their terms of use.

This project is currently in beta, not all functionality may be completely implemented.  Please report issues on any problems you find.

=== Features ===

* Download websites from a variety of sources (currently only skinnyski.com is supported)
* Compute distances and drive times to a given website based on your current location.
* Sort trail information according to most recent or nearest.
* Quick link to trail info, compose new report, and map of trail location

=== Requirements ===

Currently requires android 2.3 (gingerbread) or later.  Adding support for earlier OS versions is expected.  iOS support is not planned.

Location services are required to be enabled for computing current user location (GPS not required).

=== Installation ===

This application is currently not available on the android market.

Install the most recent .apk file from the download section of this repository.  Installing applications from outside the android market must be enabled.

